Ranger Help for: rh
====================

SYNTAX:      rh [topic]
             rhelp [topic]
             ranhelp [topic]
USAGE:       Anywhere

SUMMARY:
This command accesses the Ranger guild help system. Type 'rh' followed
by a topic to view help on that subject. Without a topic, it displays
a list of available help categories. The 'rh' command is a shorthand
alias for 'rhelp' and 'ranhelp'.

EXAMPLES:
  rh skills          - View help on Ranger skills
  rh archery         - View help on archery
  rh general         - View general guild overview
